It's been a long night, Frank.

715
00:43:14,140 --> 00:43:15,430
我得回家了
I need to get home.

716
00:43:15,430 --> 00:43:17,370
得了  賞個臉吧
Come on. Do me the honor.

717
00:43:19,510 --> 00:43:20,580
今晚不行
Not tonight.

718
00:44:41,080 --> 00:44:42,550
道格  打扮得真帥
Doug! Don't you look good.

719
00:44:42,550 --> 00:44:43,870
謝謝您  副總統女士
Thank you, Madam Vice President.

720
00:44:43,870 --> 00:44:45,100
你見到弗蘭西斯了嗎
Have you seen Francis?

721
00:44:45,100 --> 00:44:46,530
好一會兒沒見著了  女士
Not for a little while, no, ma'am.

722
00:44:46,530 --> 00:44:47,450
大家在紛紛離開了
Well, the party's breaking up.

723
00:44:47,450 --> 00:44:49,570
