I want him to say goodbye to people.

724
00:44:49,570 --> 00:44:51,900
-好  女士  我去找他  -道格
- Yes, ma'am. I'll let him know. - Doug?

725
00:44:53,200 --> 00:44:55,760
我有個問題問你  就一件小事
I have a question for you. Just a small thing.

726
00:44:55,940 --> 00:44:58,820
-怎么了  -你怎么沒去看砍頭
- What is it? - Why weren't you at the beheading?

727
00:44:59,540 --> 00:45:02,230
-什么  -詹姆斯·米勒被砍頭那晚
- What? - The night James Miller was beheaded.

728
00:45:02,770 --> 00:45:04,740
我們都在  我們四個
We were all there, the four of us.

729
00:45:04,740 --> 00:45:07,900
弗蘭西斯  湯姆  莉安和我
Francis, Tom, LeAnn and myself.

730
00:45:07,900 --> 00:45:09,020
你怎么不在
Why not you?

731
00:45:10,780 --> 00:45:13,100
你見到弗蘭西斯  就說我找他
You see Francis, tell him I'm looking for him.

732
00:45:13,820 --> 00:45:14,780
是  女士
Yes, ma'am.

733
00:45:30,990 --> 00:45:32,620
我以為你迷路了
I thought you got lost.

734
00:45:32,620 --> 00:45:35,200
不  我就想歇歇
No. I just needed a break.

735
00:45:36,250 --> 00:45:38,090
我們要去跟客人道別嗎
Shall we bid our guests farewell?

736
00:45:38,090 --> 00:45:39,710
不  今晚還早呢
No, the night is young.

737
00:45:41,660 --> 00:45:42,950
看我找到了什么
Look what I found.

738
00:45:54,390 --> 00:45:56,350
他們要重啟委員會
They're restarting the committee.

739
00:45:58,360 --> 00:46:00,440
我以為我們扼殺了那個委員會
I thought we killed that committee.

740
00:46:01,120 --> 00:46:03,080
眾議院什么都野火燒不盡
Nothing ever really dies in the House.

741
00:46:03,080 --> 00:46:07,680
只不過關注的人越來越少
It just plays in front of a smaller and smaller audience.

742
00:46:10,970 --> 00:46:13,900
-這事可不小  -我知道
- This is serious. - I know.

743
00:46:15,180 --> 00:46:17,420
但我們還是好好享受舞會吧
But let's enjoy the rest of the party.

744
00:46:45,670 --> 00:46:47,090
你是做什么的
What do you do here?

745
00:46:48,960 --> 00:46:50,240
我為他們工作
I work for them.

746
00:46:54,700 --> 00:46:57,140
總統讓我確保你安全回家
The president asked me to make sure that you get home safely.

747
00:46:57,140 --> 00:46:58,280
我給你安排了一輛車
I have a car for you.

748
00:46:58,720 --> 00:47:00,380
我還想多待一會兒
I thought I'd stay a little while longer.

749
00:47:00,380 --> 00:47:02,150
總統明天早上要早起
The president has an early morning tomorrow.

750
00:47:02,150 --> 00:47:03,230
這邊請
Right this way.

751
00:47:25,510 --> 00:47:27,050
那個導游
The tour guide?

752
00:47:31,040 --> 00:47:33,060
-什么  -是的
- What?  - Yes.

753
00:47:33,550 --> 00:47:37,350
搞什么  我應該拿那個導游怎么辦呢
WTF. What am I supposed to do about the tour guide?

754
00:47:39,730 --> 00:47:42,090
還在媒體接待室  湯姆  不是吧
The press briefing room, Tom, really?

755
00:47:45,970 --> 00:47:47,890
我以為沒人會在意
I didn't think anyone would care.

756
00:47:48,810 --> 00:47:52,230
那我是該留下她還是讓她走人呢
Well, should I... keep her on or let her go?

757
00:47:52,230 --> 00:47:55,960
她這樣做是很不專業的
I mean, it was rather unprofessional on her part.

758
00:47:58,930 --> 00:48:00,520
她很擅長她的工作
She's good at her job.

759
00:48:04,380 --> 00:48:05,460
湯姆...
Tom...

760
00:48:06,640 --> 00:48:08,580
不要對我妻子不忠
don't cheat on my wife.

761
00:48:32,510 --> 00:48:33,750
巴恩斯先生
Mr. Barnes?

762
00:48:36,540 --> 00:48:40,740
你想到別的地方喝杯咖啡嗎
Do you want to get a coffee somewhere away from this?

763
00:48:42,050 --> 00:48:43,790
我一直在想你說的話
I keep thinking about what you said.

764
00:48:48,680 --> 00:48:50,430
我在她的東西中找到了這個
I found this with her things.

765
00:48:52,780 --> 00:48:53,960
父親節那天
It was Father's Day...

766
00:48:55,020 --> 00:48:56,690
是我最后一次跟她通話
the last time I heard from her.

767
00:48:57,050 --> 00:48:58,850
我們不是很親近
We weren't close.

768
00:48:59,550 --> 00:49:01,020
我很驚訝她會打電話給我
I was surprised she called.

769
00:49:02,340 --> 00:49:04,670
我當然很開心  但是...
I mean, I was happy, of course, but...

770
00:49:06,250 --> 00:49:07,770
我能留著這個嗎
Can I hold on to this?

771
00:49:13,060 --> 00:49:14,200
我不知道
I didn't know...

772
00:49:16,310 --> 00:49:17,600
她有麻煩了
that she was in trouble.

773
00:49:20,440 --> 00:49:22,400
當警察問我她是不是有自殺傾向的時候
When the police asked if i thought she was suicidal,

774
00:49:22,400 --> 00:49:24,840
我說  "可能吧"
I said, "Maybe."

775
00:49:29,110 --> 00:49:30,570
我并不了解她
I didn't know her, really.

776
00:49:32,400 --> 00:49:33,590
我也是
Neither did I.

777
00:49:37,050 --> 00:49:38,650
我會調查這個的
I'll look into this.

778
00:49:41,040 --> 00:49:41,970
好
Okay.

779
00:49:43,250 --> 00:49:44,280
謝謝你
Thank you.

780
00:49:57,950 --> 00:50:01,000
政治新聞網  《早安喬》上說了五分鐘
Politico. Five minutes on Morning Joe.

781
