784
00:50:06,980 --> 00:50:09,100
來考慮一下你的職業選擇
to consider your career options.

785
00:50:09,360 --> 00:50:11,840
得看上去像真的才行  你知道的
This has to look real. You know that.

786
00:50:12,810 --> 00:50:14,370
如果他們要和我見面怎么辦
What if they need to meet with me?

787
00:50:16,500 --> 00:50:17,830
那他們就會和你見面
Then they'll meet with you.

788
00:50:27,050 --> 00:50:29,100
我可以叫保安護送你出去
I could have security escort you out.

789
00:50:38,040 --> 00:50:40,440
那么既然現在厄舍是特別顧問了
So since Usher is special advisor now,

790
00:50:40,440 --> 00:50:42,010
那你又算什么呢
where does that leave you?

791
00:50:45,590 --> 00:50:48,610
我說過了  如果有需要  他們會給打你的
Like I said, they'll call you if they need you.

792
00:50:53,860 --> 00:50:56,730
我可以成為你的朋友的  知道嗎
I can be a friend to you, you know.

793
00:50:57,680 --> 00:50:59,340
不必這樣的
It doesn't have to be like this.

794
00:50:59,340 --> 00:51:00,750
我沒有朋友
I don't have any friends.

795
00:51:17,080 --> 00:51:20,480
我把他安排在了巴黎的約旦大使館
I landed him at the Jordanian Embassy in Paris.

796
00:51:21,940 --> 00:51:23,960
我們計劃什么時候把他弄出來
When do we plan to get him out?

797
00:51:24,800 --> 00:51:27,450
據我所知  現在還不知道
Well, as I understand it, you don't yet know

798
00:51:27,460 --> 00:51:30,480
麥卡倫先生可能告訴了佩特羅夫總統些什么
what Mr. Macallan may have told President Petrov.

799
00:51:30,480 --> 00:51:33,450
我要麥卡倫回來  越快越好
I want Macallan back here sooner rather than later.

800
00:51:34,100 --> 00:51:37,400
這些事不發生在美國境內會更好些
It's better if these things don't happen on American soil.

801
00:51:37,870 --> 00:51:39,980
是  但我決定了
Yes, but I make those decisions.

802
00:51:39,980 --> 00:51:41,790
當然  總統先生
Of course, Mr. President.

803
00:51:43,360 --> 00:51:44,480
請放心
And rest assured,

804
00:51:44,480 --> 00:51:47,510
這件事是查不到你們身上的
neither of your fingerprints are anywhere near this.

805
00:51:55,690 --> 00:51:57,600
我們怎么處理莉安
So what do we do about LeAnn?

806
00:51:59,860 --> 00:52:04,290
她參與了選舉舞弊  天吶
She's been involved in election fraud, for Christ's sake.

807
00:52:05,510 --> 00:52:07,300
她犯了很多錯
She's made a lot of mistakes.

808
00:52:08,880 --> 00:52:11,070
是的  但很多人都犯過
Yes, but lots of people have.

809
00:52:11,070 --> 00:52:13,670
話是那么說  但有些人就走到頭了
Yes, but some people run their course.

810
00:52:16,760 --> 00:52:19,050
如今真難知道能相信誰
It's hard to know who to trust these days.

811
00:52:19,930 --> 00:52:20,970
可不是嘛
Isn't it?

